    <section id="download" class="about-section text-center">
        <div class="container">

            
            <div class="row mt">
                <div class="col-lg-1 centered">
                    <i class="fa fa-certificate"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <h3>Sign Up</h3>
                    <p>When you sign up we ask you a few questions on your background and you're set. We'll show you jobs based on your expierence.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-1 centered">
                    <i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <h3>Submit</h3>
                    <p>Take a look through the postings we've pulled together for you. You can search by date and referal fee. See a job where you'd know someone who fit in and submit. The more qualified candidates you refer the better you look to hiring managers.</p>
                </div>
            
            
                <div class="col-lg-1 centered">
                    <i class="fa fa-globe"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <h3>What's Next?</h3>
                    <p>We'll send a note to your propesctive applicant to see if they're interested. If they are the application gets routed to the hiring manager. If they hire them you get the referal fee listed on the posting.</p>
                </div>
            
            </div><!-- row -->
        </div><!-- container -->
